reviewText: Endless hours of entertainment for small children
Fast shipping and item as described
2 year old granddaughter thinks she is a ballerina because of these
My 2 year old daughter absolutely loves Angelina Ballerina. It's nice to have the three DVDs with multiple episodes per disc; it keeps things new and interesting for her short attention span!
A gift to my grand daughter. She enjoys it.
Great dvd, keeps my child dancing and smiling and dancing.  The three pack is a great price for getting three dvd's in one package
The Three videos are a good varirty of a new show to my kids.  I hope more bundle sets come out.
My 4 year old loves this DVD set.  I also like that each DVD has several different short episodes, so it seems like even more shows.
